Program: Omnibus
Title: Alexander Pope
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jhp
Last Broadcast Date: 04 May 1988
'To err is human to forgive is divine'. A profile and analysis of the very quotable British poet with contributions from Indian poet Vikram Seth, Australian poet Peter Porter, British politician Malcolm Rifkind, and Pope's biographer Maynard Mack